        </formalpara>
        <formalpara>
            <title>Concepts</title>
            <para>Concepts mentioned in this book are included in <xref linkend="solor_references"/>, and concepts, such as <xref linkend="f251d463-f346-340a-b17c-d4a4622c7a91" annotations="systolic blood pressure (observable entity)"/>. The xml:id of the
                concept is a UUID of the concept. xref elements should use the annotations attribute
                to provide a human readable representation of the concept, preferably the fully
                specified name of the concept. In <xref linkend="solor_references"/>, concepts are
                represented as glossentry elements, with the fully-specified name of the concept
                represented as a glossterm element, and the preferred name of the concept
                represented as an acronym </para>
